{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3b59b1a228","title":"关于将捕人杀人的批准权一律提高一级的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"abab1ab6d8","index":0,"year":1951,"month":5,"day":16,"articleId":"3b59b1a228"}],"tags":[{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"4bdf7f9cc1","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"3b59b1a228","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"子恢，即邓子恢，当时任中共中央中南局第三书记。"},{"id":"f3a280c73d","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"3b59b1a228","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"饶，指饶激石，当时任中共中央华东局第一书记。邓，指邓小平，当时任中共中央西南局第一书记。习，指习仲勋，当时任中共中央西北局第一书记。"}],"contents":[{"id":"6f68bfc9ba","type":"title","text":"关于将捕人杀人的批准权一律提高一级的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"3b59b1a228"},{"id":"4bdf7f9cc1","type":"paragraph","text":"子恢同志，并告饶、邓、习","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"3b59b1a228"},{"id":"f3a280c73d","type":"paragraph","text":"五月十一日电收到。为了不使步骤混乱难于掌握（自前中南西南两区已有难于掌握的形势，必须严重注意），捕人系人的批准权必须一律提高一级，不许有例外。在土改区可由省派代表至专区，由专区派代表至县，掌握材料，用电话向专区请示批准捕人，向省请示批准系人，这样对于捕系少数人仍是便利的。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"3b59b1a228"},{"id":"453a54ad3f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"3b59b1a228"},{"id":"13466cc27d","type":"paragraph","text":"五月十六日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"3b59b1a228"}],"page":{"id":"defe125ac7","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"3b59b1a228","start":309,"end":309}}}},"__N_SSG":true}